Package com.sun.identity.liberty.ws.interfaces

Provides interfaces common to all liberty services.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Authorizer This class Authorizer is an interface for identity service to check authorization of a WSC.
ResourceIDMapper The class ResourceIDMapper is an interface that is used to map between an userID and the ResourceID associated with it.
ServiceInstanceUpdate This class ServiceInstanceUpdate is an interface to include the SOAP Header namely ServiceInstanceUpdateHeader when sending a SOAP Response while processing the service request.
